      <title>曾经稀有的真菌疾病在一个没有准备的世界中杀死了数百万</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/invasive-fungal-diseases-kill-millions-pose-growing-threat-to-unprepared-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当大多数人想到危险的感染时，他们会想象细菌或病毒。但是，对于像彼得·钦港（Peter Chin-hong）这样的传染病专家而言，今天潜伏在医院和诊所中最阴险的威胁之一是真菌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/invasive-fungal-diseases-kill-millions-pose-growing-threat-to-unprepared-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
